                        "img_caption": 'The four Unit Telescopes that form the VLT together with the four Auxiliary Telescopes',
                        "src_google_map": "https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3626.8973618291066!2d-70.40635538603341!3d-24.62722218416445!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x96a54b61d20df8a7%3A0xffc2d3eef16a026b!2sVery%20Large%20Telescope!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1629797120545!5m2!1svi!2s",
